{"id": 952, "genre": 1001, "title": "哪种情况会让你觉得 “too much”？", "description": "人生法则：戴新流行的王冠配饰时最好不要把头发盘起来，会显得太“满”…即使出门前在镜子前挑了三小时，也要搭出刚睡醒收拾十分钟就出门的随意感。 （题图来自：Victor Beuren）", "record_count": 5977, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160703181347JZVm9v1N0ADxTMqL.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-05-13T11:18:46Z", "options": [{"id": 77568, "content": "别人只要一说话，不管说了什么都先说一句，不对吧，不是的，不可能。。然后就balabala?", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606461}, {"id": 78080, "content": "明明就想剪个头发，造型师非要让你要么烫下，要么染下。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607900}, {"id": 77569, "content": "现实一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 148156}, {"id": 77570, "content": "得理不饶人的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 345592}, {"id": 77571, "content": "有事没事的摆臭脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606468}, {"id": 77827, "content": "动不动就说自己是逗逼，，其实都是装逼", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182533Wvk59dqYelJCHsxw.jpg", "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 607093}, {"id": 77572, "content": "天天说自己心情不好，不知道哪那么多忧愁", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 526965}, {"id": 77573, "content": "一包药都懒得去拿给，每天说好多遍“我爱你”的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 599138}, {"id": 77574, "content": "iOS的更新提醒⏰", "image": null, "praise_count": 38, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 245811}, {"id": 77575, "content": "那些自以为是完全不顾别人感受的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 606471}, {"id": 78087, "content": "散播鸡汤文，并且觉得自己很完美的货", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 604408}, {"id": 77576, "content": "每逢过年就一堆亲戚围堵婚嫁之事", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 558568}, {"id": 77577, "conten